    "Title": "Green light on ~mission(TargetName|Last)",
    "TitleKey": "headhunters_EliminateSpecific_Generic_VH_title_001",
    "DisplayTitle": "Green light on [TargetName|Last]",
    "Description": "Word's come down through my bosses that we're settling old debts. I've got an open line on this old-time hitter named ~mission(TargetName) who's racked up a hefty kill list. We caught wind that they were hiding out with some people over at ~mission(Location|Address) who aren't the biggest fans of us, so they probably won't take kindly to you. ~mission(TargetName|Last) is the target here, but you might have to mix it up with them.\n\nAgain, whenever we've tried to take out ~mission(TargetName|Last), they've killed their killer. I feel like you'll fare better, but I'd bring backup if you got it.\n\nGood luck.\n\n-Stows",
    "DescriptionKey": "headhunters_EliminateSpecific_Generic_VH_desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "Word's come down through my bosses that we're settling old debts. I've got an open line on this old-time hitter named [TargetName] who's racked up a hefty kill list. We caught wind that they were hiding out with some people over at Last Ditch who aren't the biggest fans of us, so they probably won't take kindly to you. [TargetName|Last] is the target here, but you might have to mix it up with them.\n\nAgain, whenever we've tried to take out [TargetName|Last], they've killed their killer. I feel like you'll fare better, but I'd bring backup if you got it.\n\nGood luck.\n\n-Stows",
